              <ol>
                  <li>
                      <span>api ➞ CSSNestedDeclarations
                      	<a href="https://drafts.csswg.org/css-nesting-1/#cssnesteddeclarations"><img src="https://bcd-watch.igalia.com/imgs/spec2.svg" alt="Spec link"></a>
