                    <b><br></b> 
                    <span class="browsers">Added to <strong>Safari</strong></span> 
                    <b>&nbsp;➞&nbsp;</b>
                    <span class="ni3 engines"><strong>3 of 3</strong> engines</span>

                  </li>
                  <li>
                      <span>api ➞ CSSNestedDeclarations ➞ style
                      	<a href="https://drafts.csswg.org/css-nesting-1/#dom-cssnesteddeclarations-style"><img src="https://bcd-watch.igalia.com/imgs/spec2.svg" alt="Spec link"></a>
                      </span>

          

                    
                    <b><br></b> 
                    <span class="browsers">Added to <strong>Safari</strong></span> 
                    <b>&nbsp;➞&nbsp;</b>
                    <span class="ni3 engines"><strong>3 of 3</strong> engines</span>

                  </li>
                  <li>

          

                      <span>
                        <a href="https://developer.mozilla.org/docs/Web/API/Element/auxclick_event">api ➞ Element ➞ auxclick_event</a>
                      </span>
                    
                    <b><br></b> 
                    <span class="browsers">Added to <strong>Safari</strong></span> 
                    <b>&nbsp;➞&nbsp;</b>
                    <span class="ni3 engines"><strong>3 of 3</strong> engines</span>

                  </li>
              </ol>
	            <h4>CSS</h4>
