                  <li>
                      <span>css ➞ properties ➞ ruby-position ➞ over
                      </span>

          

                    
                    <b><br></b> 
                    <span class="browsers">Added to <strong>Safari</strong></span> 
                    <b>&nbsp;➞&nbsp;</b>
                    <span class="ni3 engines"><strong>3 of 3</strong> engines</span>

                  </li>
                  <li>
                      <span>css ➞ properties ➞ ruby-position ➞ under
                      </span>

          

                    
                    <b><br></b> 
                    <span class="browsers">Added to <strong>Safari</strong></span> 
                    <b>&nbsp;➞&nbsp;</b>
                    <span class="ni3 engines"><strong>3 of 3</strong> engines</span>

                  </li>
                  <li>
                      <span>css ➞ properties ➞ text-underline-offset ➞ percentage
                      	<a href="https://drafts.csswg.org/css-text-decor-4/#valdef-text-underline-offset-percentage"><img src="https://bcd-watch.igalia.com/imgs/spec2.svg" alt="Spec link"></a>
                      </span>

          

                    
                    <b><br></b> 
                    <span class="browsers">Added to <strong>Safari</strong></span> 
                    <b>&nbsp;➞&nbsp;</b>
                    <span class="ni3 engines"><strong>3 of 3</strong> engines</span>

